    <title>初识HTML</title>
    <url>/posts/b2426900.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML"></a>HTML</h3><blockquote>
<p>HTML是一种用来描述网页的超文本语言，也是构成网页文档的主要语言。</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="HTML的主要网页结构"><a href="#HTML的主要网页结构" class="headerlink" title="HTML的主要网页结构"></a>HTML的主要网页结构</h4><p> 1.header标签:头部分结构<br> 2.nav标签:导航条部分结构<br> 3.main标签:主核心部分内容<br> 4.footer标签:页尾</p>
<p>代码示例：</p>
<pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html">1 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
2 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>header</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>...<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
3 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>nav</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>...<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
4 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>main</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>...<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
5 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>...<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
6 <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
</code></pre>
<h4 id="HTML的页面优化"><a href="#HTML的页面优化" class="headerlink" title="HTML的页面优化"></a>HTML的页面优化</h4><p> 1.减少网站对http的请求</p>
<p> 2.css文件写在头部</p>
<p> 3.javascript文件写在尾部或者异步</p>
<p> 4.减少dom节点</p>
<p> 5.减少重绘和回流</p>
<p> 6.压缩图片 </p>
<blockquote>
<p>png: 无损压缩的图片格式  带透明通道 （小图）      jpeg  有损压缩 （大图）     gif  带透明通道   带动态通道  有损压缩的格式（动图）</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
